tence\": \"- is an enormous source of pride,\\\" said Geste, who wears 25-centimetre (10-inch) heels when in full costume.\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1117, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an enormous source\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1032}, {\"ngram\": \"pride\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1041}, {\"ngram\": \"Geste\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1054}, {\"ngram\": \"25-centimetre (10-inch) heels\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1095}, {\"ngram\": \"full costume\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1116}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"One of the messages that I want to carry is the pride in my community because 10 years ago having a drag queen carry the torch would have been unimaginable,\\\" added the campaigner for the LGBTQIA+ community.\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1326, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the messages\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1139}, {\"ngram\": \"the pride\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1173}, {\"ngram\": \"my community\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1189}, {\"ngram\": \"a drag queen\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1230}, {\"ngram\": \"the torch\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1246}, {\"ngram\": \"the campaigner\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1298}, {\"ngram\": \"the LGBTQIA+ community\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said performing as a drag queen in corsets and high heels was physically demanding, \\\"but not yet an Olympic sport\\\", adding she had previously done wrestling and synchronised swimming.\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1515, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a drag queen\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1363}, {\"ngram\": \"corsets\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1374}, {\"ngram\": \"high heels\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1389}, {\"ngram\": \"wrestling\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1488}, {\"ngram\": \"synchronised swimming\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Far-right politician Marion Marechal said Geste was responsible for \\\"particularly vulgar\\\" and \\\"hyper-sexualised performances\\\".\", \"from\":